  <p style="font-size: 22px; margin-top: 16px;">
    A curated selection of product, platform, and systems work spanning enterprise
    transformation, service ecosystems, and AI-native experience design.
  </p>

  <div style="margin-top: 32px; border-top: 1px solid var(--divider);"></div>

  <section style="margin-top: 48px;">

    <article style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <h2>
        <a href="/case-studies/smb-marketplace-fintech" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
          SMB Marketplace & Fintech Ecosystem
        </a>
      </h2>
      <p>
        Designing an integrated marketplace and financial services ecosystem for small
        and medium-sized businesses in Latin America.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <h2>
        <a href="/case-studies/ai-life-sciences-platform" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
          AI-Powered Life Sciences Platform
        </a>
      </h2>
      <p>
        Shaping a complex platform experience that helped scientific teams work more
        efficiently with intelligent tools and structured workflows.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <h2>
        <a href="/case-studies/global-servicing-platform" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
          Global Servicing Platform
